<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #718096; text-align: center; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #3b82f6; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Aarogentix!</h1>
    </div>
    <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
    <p>Congratulations! Your healthcare organization, <strong>{{organizationName}}</strong>, is now active on Aarogentix.</p>
    <p>You can now start managing patients, appointments, and billing with ease.</p>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{url}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </div>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2026 Aarogentix. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
